    <p class="label mb-6">About</p>

    <h2 class="section-title mb-5" style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.02em; max-width: 24ch;">
      I don't just ship products. I build the teams that ship them.
